These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, martial-arts
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching zombie movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | martial-arts | zombie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, snooker
1. the person playing chess is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing snooker##2
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Game   | snooker | chess | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
House: townhouse, futuristic, craftsman
1. the futuristic house is between the townhouse house and the craftsman house##2
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| House   | craftsman | futuristic | townhouse |

 #################################

 
