.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, red, yellow
1. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes red##2
2. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Color   | red | brown | yellow |

